The '''Kuchu Collective''' is a [[non governmental organization]] that aims to promote and protect [[LGBTI]] [[rights]] in sub-Saharan Africa by developing and actively encouraging use of technological tools and materials, that shield LGBTI persons and activists against [[hate groups]], repressive [[governments]] and their institutions .<ref>Kuchu Collective. [http://kuchucollective.com/ Our Mission]. Retrieved 2015-7-18</ref>
