'''''The Transformation of the School: Progressivism in American Education, 1876–1957''''' is a history of the American [[Progressive Education]] movement<!-- from 1876 to 1957,--> written by historian [[Lawrence Cremin]] and published by [[Alfred A. Knopf]] in 1961.{{sfn|Hart|1962}}

